1️⃣ User signs up → Enters email and receives an OTP for verification.
2️⃣ User logs in → OTP is required again for authentication.
3️⃣ User accesses features (hide/unhide file)

1️⃣ Hiding a File (hideFiles)
✔ Reads the file from the system.
✔ Converts it into binary format (LONGBLOB) and stores it in MySQL.
✔ Deletes the file from the local system after successful storage.

2️⃣ Unhiding a File (unhide)
✔ Retrieves the hidden file from MySQL using file ID.
✔ Saves the retrieved file back to the system.
